pageProduct.name: Thompson's Brewer's Yeast 100 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's Brewer's Yeast provides a rich source of nutrients to help support general wellbeing.

Thompson's Brewer's Yeast provides a rich source of nutrients such as B vitamins to help support general wellbeing.

Size: 100tabs

KEY FEATURES

• Nourish the body.
• Support general health and wellbeing.
• Vegetarian friendly.

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional. Contains Gluten, Sulphites.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each tablet contains:
Yeast dried (Brewer's Yeast) 500mg AD83

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place. Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken. Keep out of reach of children.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
